metadata.description:
The first of the BBVERSE series is 𝒞𝓁𝒾𝒸𝓀 𝒻𝑜𝓇 𝒶 𝒮𝓊𝓇𝓅𝓇𝒾𝓈𝑒 - 01 featuring '𝓕𝓊𝒸𝓀 𝓎𝑜𝓊 BB'

The angsty one of the lot. Hates excessive consumerism but shops at Net-a-Porter for the same day delivery. Lives off triple shot espressos. Judgmental but means well. Binges Instagram Reels to drown out existential dread.
